name: Analog Journey - Genesis
description: All bits carry more than just data. Each conglomerate of information contains a story urging to be contemplated. Machines are enchanted dreamcatchers and we are the potion sellers. Made on June 2020, this was a succesful attempt of joining my university teacher's gamejam team. We ended up working together on LDJAM (https://ldjam.com/events/ludum-dare/46/dads-breath).
